                    <p class="s_product_catalog_dish_title d-flex align-items-baseline pb-2">&#13;
                        <span class="s_product_catalog_dish_name s_product_catalog_dish_dot_leaders">Farm Friendly Chicken Supreme</span>&#13;
                        <span class="s_product_catalog_dish_price ms-auto ps-2">$15.50</span>&#13;
                    </p>&#13;
                </li>&#13;
                <li class="s_product_catalog_dish" data-name="Product">&#13;
